    "body": "### Language server\n\nlua-language-server\n\n### Requested feature\n\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nSo for example I have a lua file with a grammar error. The keyword _function_ is misspelled (letter 'f' is missing):\r\n\r\n```\r\nunction ()\r\n\r\nend\r\n```\r\nWhen I open this file with nvim, treesitter does not throw errors or warnings like it should.\r\nTo get the Diagnostics finally to start I have to manually **:e!** in nvim to trigger treesitter to reparse this buffer.\r\nOnly then I get warnings/errors.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nAutomatically reparse newly opened files so that Diagnostics shows errors/warnings just in case.\r\n\r\n\n\n### Other clients which have this feature\n\n_No response_",
